propList.Name: dataSource
propList.Description: Used for setting the source data. The elements that are part of this array will be present the left column. Except the elements whose keys are included in targetKeys prop

propList.Name: disabled
propList.Description: Whether disabled transfer

propList.Name: filterOption
propList.Description: A function to determine whether an item should show in search result list

propList.Name: footer
propList.Description: A function used for rendering the footer

propList.Name: listStyle
propList.Description: A custom CSS style used for rendering the transfer columns

propList.Name: locale
propList.Description: The i18n text including filter, empty text, item unit, etc
propList.Type: { itemUnit: string; itemsUnit: string; searchPlaceholder: string; notFoundContent: ReactNode; }
propList.Default: { itemUnit: item, itemsUnit: items, notFoundContent: The list is empty, searchPlaceholder: Search here }

propList.Name: oneWay
propList.Description: Display as single direction style

propList.Name: operations
propList.Description: A set of operations that are sorted from top to bottom

propList.Name: operationStyle
propList.Description: A custom CSS style used for rendering the operations column

propList.Name: pagination
propList.Description: Use pagination. Not work in render props

propList.Name: render
propList.Description: The function to generate the item shown on a column. Based on an record (element of the dataSource array), this function should return a React element which is generated from that record. Also, it can return a plain object with value and label, label is a React element and value is for title

propList.Name: selectAllLabels
propList.Description: A set of customized labels for select all checkboxs on the header

propList.Name: selectedKeys
propList.Description: A set of keys of selected items

propList.Name: showSearch
propList.Description: If included, a search box is shown on each column

propList.Name: showSelectAll
propList.Description: Show select all checkbox on the header

propList.Name: targetKeys
propList.Description: A set of keys of elements that are listed on the right column

propList.Name: titles
propList.Description: A set of titles that are sorted from left to right

propList.Name: onChange
propList.Description: A callback function that is executed when the transfer between columns is complete

propList.Name: onScroll
propList.Description: A callback function which is executed when scroll options list

propList.Name: onSearch
propList.Description: A callback function which is executed when search field are changed

propList.Name: onSelectChange
propList.Description: A callback function which is executed when selected items are changed
